{"tid":938572,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我老婆大洗嘅程度真係嚇撚死我","createTime":"2018-12-12T11:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-15T12:16:48.000Z","uid":65024,"like":2,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"1adc99b4761324dbf8455f3147e19062c19b7339","tid":938572,"uid":65024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T11:59:09.000Z","msg":"尋晚上網睇下銀行條數真係眼都突埋<br />\n十一月現金洗左四萬，簽卡簽左八萬<br />\n我即刻拉佢入書房屌佢老母<br />\n居住成本、水電煤、小朋友學費已經個個月洗左我七八萬<br />\n單係過一個十一月我咪要成廿萬<br />\n我係咁屌佢，佢係咁話知道，想喊咁款<br />\n問佢洗左去邊佢就話係D細路嘅興趣班學費，平日飲飲食食，買餸錢，工人人工<br />\n我屌佢唔學野會死?無工人會死?買餸唔洗咩都買貴野下化!?<br />\n呢類問題我前前後後已經同佢講過好多年<br />\n試過cut佢附屬卡最後心軟又同佢開返<br />\n唉&hellip;&hellip;有時真係心淡到想同佢離婚算"},{"pid":"02e4d4bdcaa079c68147b4dec10bcb8e56a49a77","tid":938572,"uid":138138,"like":91,"dislike":0,"score":91,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"我都想信你，可惜你係一個假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cec501cd6768f427ae56339893b036fda7fa2ed","tid":938572,"uid":24044,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:01:03.000Z","msg":"你自己心軟，有咩好講呢？"},{"pid":"11b7f70e74f835f535a50288dde797c85ef2b135","tid":938572,"uid":114014,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"辛辛苦苦搵啲錢返黎，又有隻係米缸倒米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n師兄真係慘。"},{"pid":"f487db3b59feb91df0d3fa63d666fa535e6ad8f8","tid":938572,"uid":69886,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:02:15.000Z","msg":"拎d錢去叫雞好過"},{"pid":"89862dd83c6bfc6b960ced6d4ba6ab3eccacf701","tid":938572,"uid":65024,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"02e4d4bdcaa079c68147b4dec10bcb8e56a49a77","tid":938572,"uid":138138,"like":91,"dislike":0,"score":91,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:00:43.000Z","msg":"我都想信你，可惜你係一個假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:07:40.000Z","msg":"呃你有獎咩師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/n